Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.49,0:00:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.13,0:00:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail! I won't let you get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.07,0:00:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.15,0:00:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,-You two go after that one!\N-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.96,0:00:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.28,0:00:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You thought I'd get tricked\Nwith your magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.72,0:00:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Today I'll get you for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.31,0:00:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.89,0:00:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The next time, I'll have\Ncomplete data on you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.26,0:00:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,...and you won't get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.74,0:01:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,STEAL THE MEMORABLE HARMONICA!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.22,0:01:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyuki, please cheer up.\NI'm sure God is with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.40,0:01:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.16,0:01:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Music competition?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.10,0:01:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. They're holding the Seika City\NYouth Music Competition tonight...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.31,0:01:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,...at the new hall that opened\Non Bayside Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.32,0:01:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And Miyuki is one\Nof the contestants, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.86,0:01:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But a problem has come up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.40,0:01:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by a "problem"?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.34,0:01:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyuki was supposed to play\Na harmonica at the contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.32,0:01:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But a certain person has tricked her\Nand taken her harmonica.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.20,0:02:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Tricked her and taken it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.13,0:02:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.11,0:02:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,FUKUYAMA MUSIC INSTRUMENTS
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.11,0:02:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,To have the harmonica tuned...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.02,0:02:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,...Miyuki took it\Nto a music store on First Avenue.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.09,0:02:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,A music store on First Avenue\Nmeans it's the shop owned...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.47,0:02:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,...by Mr. Fukuyama,\None of the city's wealthy citizens.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.34,0:02:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But Miyuki's harmonica was switched...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.88,0:02:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...with a fake one by that Fukuyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.07,0:02:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,She isn't the only one he's deceived.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.71,0:02:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He's tricked others, taken\Ntheir instruments and sold them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.12,0:02:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What an unforgivable thing to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.03,0:02:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyuki's harmonica is\Na rare foreign-made one...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.97,0:02:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,...given to her by her late father.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.88,0:02:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,She's used it\Nsince she was little, so--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.35,0:02:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,She won't perform as well\Non another harmonica.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.39,0:03:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. You have to get her harmonica\Nback by the time the contest begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.44,0:03:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to help Miyuki give a\Nsuccessful performance, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.39,0:03:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm starved.\NLet's grab a few hamburgers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.53,0:03:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'll pass on it today.\N-Then how about a game?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.98,0:03:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I've got some things to do.\NSorry, but I'm heading home. See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.05,0:03:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail? This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.93,0:03:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Rats! She's teasing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.17,0:03:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,NICE JOB - ST. TAIL
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.58,0:03:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.82,0:04:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,"Tonight I'm taking a harmonica\Nin the First Avenue music store."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.53,0:04:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What? St. Tail, you--!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.51,0:04:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-Dad!\N-Son, sorry, but your dinner's pizza.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.22,0:04:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No time for dinner!\NTonight, St. Tail's gonna--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.89,0:04:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Calling me in for backup when\NI'm off duty. What a rotten deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.83,0:04:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The First Avenue music store,\NSt. Tail's--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.81,0:04:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay.\NOh, I almost forgot something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.19,0:04:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,A photo of the man we're guarding.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.79,0:04:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The chairman of the panel of judges\Nfor the music competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.23,0:04:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Wilson, famous composer\Nand competitor in music contests.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.58,0:04:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I've got to involve myself\Nin international affairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.42,0:04:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I better not forget\Nto get his signature.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.49,0:04:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Dad! Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.43,0:04:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Please forgive me\Nfor not being finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.98,0:04:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,My, that's a cute doll!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.85,0:05:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.12,0:05:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,-This is Daddy.\N-That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.19,0:05:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be putting on a magic\Nshow at the hall on Bayside Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.51,0:05:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The hall on Bayside Street?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.11,0:05:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's a magic show\Nat such a grand hall...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.39,0:05:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,...that I've got to put together\Nquite a gimmick.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.56,0:05:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm using miniatures\Nto plan out the whole setup.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.20,0:05:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-What magic will you be doing?\N-A great escape act.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.61,0:05:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,A great escape act? Wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.38,0:05:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a little escape route\Nunder the stage of that hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.33,0:05:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm planning to use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.20,0:05:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's called "Escape From Flames."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.01,0:05:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,-An escape from water may be better.\N-You have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.08,0:05:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,With Mom's ideas\Nand Dad's magic put together...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.52,0:05:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,...it'll probably be a wonderful show!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.30,0:05:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,-Ruby expects it to be fabulous too.\N-Thank you, Ruby.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.75,0:06:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Lord, forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.44,0:06:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.98,0:06:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.18,0:06:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.15,0:06:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyuki is scheduled\Nto perform at 8:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.59,0:06:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,8:00. I've got to hurry\Nor I won't make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.23,0:06:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.48,0:06:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,May the blessings of God be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.29,0:06:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What? The schedule has changed?\NThat's a problem. What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.23,0:06:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Fukuyama, I simply will not\Nbe able to meet you at your shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.84,0:07:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, my next performance\Nwas suddenly moved up...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.85,0:07:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...and I must leave Japan immediately\Nafter tonight's competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.66,0:07:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.63,0:07:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I will take the instrument\Ndown to the hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.61,0:07:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that would be excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.82,0:07:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then, Mr. Fukuyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.63,0:07:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Wilson, we will be arriving\Nat the hall soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.28,0:07:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,-Mr. Fukuyama, isn't it?\N-What do you want, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.42,0:07:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Asuka Jr. and I was commissioned\Nto help catch St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.07,0:07:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I received a notice\Nthat St. Tail will come...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.27,0:07:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,...to steal a harmonica in this shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.31,0:07:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail or Hail or whatever, I don't\Nknow about it! Go home, I'm busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.69,0:07:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That won't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.10,0:07:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You will cooperate\Nin staking this place out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.77,0:08:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's an official investigation\Nfrom the mayor! Do as you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.82,0:08:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.19,0:08:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That St. Tail.\NSo that's what she's after.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.20,0:08:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.33,0:08:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,She can have any harmonica\Nin the shop she wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.36,0:08:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The stolen instruments are\Nall stored right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.11,0:08:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,7:00. Okay, come from wherever\Nyou want, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.57,0:09:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail!\NYou won't get the harmonica!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.25,0:09:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Hey, the harmonica is\Nover here, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.19,0:09:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that magic again. According\Nto my analysis, the real one is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.21,0:09:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange. The storage\Nroom door was left open.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.93,0:09:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're kidding. According to Seira,\Nthe harmonica should be here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.40,0:09:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.78,0:09:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.92,0:09:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't escape today!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.32,0:09:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Where can Miyuki's harmonica be?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.18,0:10:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukuyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.49,0:10:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That wooden box! Miyuki's harmonica\Nis probably in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.49,0:10:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Where the heck is he going?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.13,0:10:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Rats! I won't let her get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.43,0:10:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ladies and gentlemen,\Nthank you for attending...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.51,0:10:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,...the Seika City Youth Music\NCompetitions this evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.58,0:10:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonight's purpose is\Nto create artists of the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.49,0:11:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We offer an opportunity to study\Nabroad to one outstanding performer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.60,0:11:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then, let me introduce to you\Nour panel of judges!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.13,0:11:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the Bayside Street Hall.\NWhat? He can't be going in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.99,0:11:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I'm pleased to introduce the\Nworld-renowned composer, Mr. Wilson!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.11,0:11:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Wilson is chairman of the panel\Nof judges for this competition!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.12,0:11:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It is time to begin our competition.\NEntry number one!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.76,0:11:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,A junior at Seika High School...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.24,0:11:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,...Megumi Hirose will be displaying\Nher talents on the piano!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.59,0:12:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn! Where's that St. Tail gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.23,0:12:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What? That's the--!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.12,0:12:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The first half is now complete.\NWe will take a 10-minute intermission.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.38,0:12:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, Mr. Wilson.\NMay I have a word with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.93,0:12:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,-And you are?\N-Fukuyama. I called you earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.87,0:12:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I appreciate you coming here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.75,0:12:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't know if you will\Nfind anything you like...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.92,0:12:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,...but I think it will be\Nworth your while.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.93,0:12:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I look forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.07,0:12:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I already prepared the instruments\Nbelow the stage of this hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.75,0:12:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.22,0:13:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He's planning to sell\NMiyuki's harmonica to Wilson here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.00,0:13:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That won't happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.50,0:13:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,-Dad!\N-Son! What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.74,0:13:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like St. Tail's\Nsneaked into this hall!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.79,0:13:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail, you said?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.56,0:13:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. She said she'd take a harmonica\Nfrom the music store...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.83,0:13:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,...but I don't know what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.44,0:13:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A harmonica.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.71,0:13:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ladies and gentlemen, the second half\Nof the competition will begin soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.89,0:13:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Please return to your seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.39,0:13:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Son, we'll talk later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.44,0:13:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail is definitely planning\Nto start something here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.25,0:13:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Where in this hall could St. Tail\Ntry to pull something off?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.13,0:13:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Under the stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.98,0:14:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good. I can't perform\Nproperly on this harmonica.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.30,0:14:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Miyuki Morishita, you're to\Nappear soon. Please get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.74,0:14:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.61,0:14:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.93,0:14:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.01,0:14:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,My data is correct.\NSt. Tail will show up if I wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.43,0:14:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Next we have Miyuki Morishita...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.27,0:15:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,...a student at St. Paulia School,\Nperforming on her harmonica.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.85,0:15:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What a fix. What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.70,0:15:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.57,0:15:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! The escape route\NDad was talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.61,0:15:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.46,0:15:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did this flower come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.30,0:15:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Now's my chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.57,0:15:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.84,0:15:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it, St. Tail! Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.41,0:15:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,-What's the matter? Are you all right?\N-It's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.09,0:15:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't perform unless\NI use my father's harmonica.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.38,0:16:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheer up, Miyuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.72,0:16:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.09,0:16:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,-St. Tail?\N-Wow! Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.46,0:16:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyuki, your precious harmonica\Nis here in the hall!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.74,0:16:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,She's over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.19,0:16:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.47,0:16:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,...show...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.24,0:16:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,...time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.93,0:16:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,-What's this?\N-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.37,0:16:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Son!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.22,0:16:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.53,0:16:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What are these instruments?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.10,0:17:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,-Don't touch them! Stop it!\N-Mr. Fukuyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.85,0:17:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't touch any of my instruments!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.06,0:17:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch! Your instruments?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.40,0:17:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the violin that\NI asked Mr. Fukuyama to repair.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.57,0:17:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's my flute!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.44,0:17:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! These are my instruments!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.72,0:17:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's it! Fukuyama stole these!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.53,0:17:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,-Son, what's this all about?\N-He's the one!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.90,0:17:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,They were probably stolen by Fukuyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.14,0:17:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.22,0:17:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.59,0:17:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.63,0:17:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are these instruments\Nthat you've stolen?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.58,0:17:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, how about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.02,0:17:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch! Yes, that right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.43,0:18:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it! St. Tail got away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.31,0:18:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Fukuyama, were you planning\Nto sell me instruments like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.73,0:18:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you attempting to deceive me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.33,0:18:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You better think of how those\Nwhose instruments were stolen feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.01,0:18:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Wilson, I will take\Nthe responsibility of returning...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.02,0:18:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,...these instruments to their owners.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.56,0:18:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyuki, now you'll be able\Nto play your best on the harmonica.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.31,0:18:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.28,0:18:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Miyuki, please perform your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.06,0:18:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The audience is eager\Nto hear you play your harmonica.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.16,0:18:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir, I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.28,0:18:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it! She's escaped again!
